<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gore1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gore,</orth> subst. blood effused from the body: <bibl n="shak. ven 664" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 664</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.346" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 346</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.6.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 6, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.82" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.3.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 3, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.5.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 5, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.484" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 484</bibl>. <cit><quote>bedaubed in blood, all in g. blood,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 56</bibl></cit> (the nurse's speech).
